He's doing all right, I guess.

27
00:01:22,410 --> 00:01:24,660
Oh, I'm glad to hear it.

28
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,580
I haven't heard from him at all lately,

29
00:01:26,580 --> 00:01:30,500
