Try not to miss her. Don't forget she's so...

33
00:03:15,570 --> 00:03:17,280
Hiyajo-san.

34
00:03:22,410 --> 00:03:25,030
Long time no see, you guys.

35
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,870
"Marbled Port-Cutlet Sandwiches"
"Chicken & Rice"

