00:03:26,410 --> 00:03:28,620
Maho-san seems to be doing well.

37
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:32,500
Yeah, apparently she came to help the Professor.

38
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:34,170
What a busy girl.

39
00:03:34,170 --> 00:03:37,250
I wonder if Kagari-chan is doing well too?

40
00:03:37,250 --> 00:03:40,720
Me too. I know Daru and
Suzuha were looking for her...

41
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:41,720
Yeah...

42
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,720
By the way, where's Hashida-san?

43
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:48,390
I guess he had something important to talk
with Suzu-meow about, so he couldn't come.

44
00:03:48,390 --> 00:03:49,560
Hmm...

45
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,020
"Television"
"CRT Workshop"

46
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,400
What the hell, Dad?!

47
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,860
